flowchart TB
    U[User klik Print] --> L1[POST print-lock]
    L1 --> C1{Lock berhasil?}

    C1 -- Tidak --> ERR1[409: sedang diprint user lain]
    ERR1 --> END[SELESAI]

    C1 -- Ya --> V[Open PDF Preview]
    V --> C2{User klik Cetak?}

    C2 -- Tidak --> RL1[DELETE print-lock]
    RL1 --> C3{DELETE sukses?}
    C3 -- Ya --> END
    C3 -- Tidak --> Q1[Queue Hive: needsReleaseLock]
    Q1 --> END

    C2 -- Ya --> WB[writeBytes ke printer]
    WB --> C4{writeBytes == true?}

    C4 -- Tidak --> RL1

    C4 -- Ya --> P1[PATCH increment HasBeenPrinted]
    P1 --> C5{PATCH sukses?}

    C5 -- Ya --> UPD[Update count lokal + socket print_confirmed]
    C5 -- Tidak --> Q2[Queue Hive: needsIncrement]

    UPD --> RL2[DELETE print-lock]
    Q2 --> RL2

    RL2 --> C6{DELETE sukses?}
    C6 -- Ya --> DONE[Queue kosong]
    C6 -- Tidak --> Q3[Queue Hive: needsReleaseLock]

    DONE --> UI1[Icon sync hilang]
    Q3 --> UI2[Icon sync muncul]

    UI2 --> WK[Worker retry periodik/resume]
    WK --> RP[Retry PATCH jika needsIncrement]
    RP --> RD[Retry DELETE jika needsReleaseLock]
    RD --> C7{Semua sukses?}
    C7 -- Ya --> UI1
    C7 -- Tidak --> WK
